    {
      "text": "%md\n\n# Employee EDA - Simple Python Version\n\nThis notebook demonstrates EDA using Python/Pandas (without PySpark).\n\n## Setup Required\n\nFirst, copy your data from HDFS to a local directory:\n\n```bash\ndocker exec namenode hdfs dfs -get /user/python-etl/employees/integrated_employees.csv /tmp/\ndocker cp namenode:/tmp/integrated_employees.csv ./data/output/\n```\n\nThen run this notebook!\n\n---",
      "user": "anonymous",
      "dateUpdated": "2026-03-19T00:00:00+0000",
